# Graeco-Latin Squares Art Generator

This project generates art from Graeco-Latin squares using mathematical constructions.

## Tech Stack
- Vite + React + TailwindCSS + shadcn UI + zustand

## UI Guidelines
- Always use shadcn components. Extend their styles when needed
- Use existing components from `components/ui/` directory
- If component doesn't exist, check shadcn catalog and install if available
- Otherwise, construct custom components on top of shadcn

## Style
- Retro but modern aesthetic
- Monochrome design
- When need gray palette, use the neutral palette
- Macintosh System 7 inspired UI feel
- Pixelated fonts

## Code Guidelines
- No comments
- Follow Rules of React
- Avoid timeouts
